/target
Cargo.lock

# Piles are user data — don't commit. `self.pile` is the conventional
# name; contributors may also create demo.pile, test.pile, etc.
*.pile
*.pile.bak-*

# Exception: bootstrap.pile is the curated onboarding substrate that
# new agents `cat` into their fresh self.pile. Sources live in
# `bootstrap/` and the pile regenerates via `bootstrap/build.sh`.
!bootstrap.pile
